Package: media-web-viewer
Version: 1.3.2
Section: multimedia
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, python3-pip, libmediainfo0v5, ffmpeg, google-chrome-stable | chromium-browser | chromium | firefox, shared-mime-info, libgdk-pixbuf2.0-0
Maintainer: kazaa3
Description: Media Web Viewer
 A local desktop application for managing and playing media files
